trans-unit.source: Implements the <c>GenerateBootstrapper</c> task.
Use the <c>GenerateBootstrapper</c> element in your project file to create and execute this task.
For usage and parameter information, see [GenerateBootstrapper Task](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ca3ba2c6-d2ea-41f2-b7e3-0fc2b0730460).
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper" /> class.
Gets or sets the file the bootstrapper will use to begin the installation of the application after all prerequisites have been installed.
The file the bootstrapper will use to begin the installation of the application after all prerequisites have been installed.
trans-unit.target: 啟動載入器將用來在安裝所有必要條件之後開始安裝應用程式的檔案。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the application that the bootstrapper will install.
The name of the application that the bootstrapper will install.
trans-unit.target: 啟動載入器將安裝的應用程式名稱。

trans-unit.source: This name will appear in the UI the bootstrapper uses during installation.
trans-unit.target: 此名稱將在安裝期間出現於啟動載入器所使用的 UI 中。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether a component runs with elevated permissions when it is installed on a target computer.
Returns <see langword="True" /> if the installed component runs with elevated permissions; otherwise <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: 傳回<see langword="True" />如果已安裝的元件執行提高權限; 否則<see langword="False" />。

trans-unit.source: This property can be set in the project file, but it is not exposed in the MSBuild schema.
trans-unit.target: 可以在專案檔中，設定這個屬性，但它不會顯示在 MSBuild 結構描述中。

trans-unit.source: In the project file's `MsiBootstrapper` section, set the [RequiresElevation Property](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6f449071-9caf-46e7-b7d4-7bbc21cf9aa7) to `True`.
trans-unit.target: 在專案檔`MsiBootstrapper`區段中，將[RequiresElevation 屬性](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6f449071-9caf-46e7-b7d4-7bbc21cf9aa7)至`True`。

trans-unit.source: A component runs with elevated permissions when it writes a registry key or is being installed to the GAC.
trans-unit.target: 寫入登錄機碼或安裝至 GAC 時，元件會以更高權限執行。

trans-unit.source: For example, if you are installing assemblies to the GAC, you need to set this property to `True`.
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果您要安裝的組件至 GAC，您需要將此屬性設定為`True`。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Web location that is hosting the application’s installer.
The Web location that is hosting the application’s installer.
trans-unit.target: 裝載應用程式安裝程式的 Web 位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the built location of bootstrapper package files.
The built location of bootstrapper package files.
trans-unit.target: 啟動載入器封裝檔案的建置位置。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.CopyComponents%2A> is `true`, the values of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.BootstrapperComponentFiles%2A> should all be based on <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.OutputPath%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.CopyComponents%2A>是`true`，值<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.BootstrapperComponentFiles%2A>應該所有根據<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.OutputPath%2A>。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.BootstrapperComponentFiles%2A> values are based on the value of the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.Path%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 否則，<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.BootstrapperComponentFiles%2A>值為基礎的值<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.Path%2A>屬性。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the products to build into the bootstrapper.
The products to build into the bootstrapper.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定要建置在啟動載入器中的產品。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the built location of setup.exe.
The built location of setup.exe.
trans-unit.target: setup.exe 的建置位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a location for the bootstrapper to look for installation prerequisites to install.
The location for the bootstrapper to look for installation prerequisites to install.
trans-unit.target: 啟動載入器用來尋找要安裝之安裝必要條件的位置。

trans-unit.source: This property can have the following values::
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性可以具有下列值::

trans-unit.source: `HomeSite`: Indicates that the prerequisite is being hosted by the component vendor.
trans-unit.target: `HomeSite`︰表示必要條件已由元件廠商所裝載。

trans-unit.source: `Relative`: Indicates that the preqrequisite is at the same location of the application.
trans-unit.target: `Relative`︰表示必要條件位於應用程式的相同位置。

trans-unit.source: `Absolute`: Indicates that all components are to be found at a centralized URL.
trans-unit.target: `Absolute`︰表示可在集中式 URL 中找到所有元件。

trans-unit.source: This value should be used in conjunction with the `ComponentsUrl` property.
trans-unit.target: 這個值應該用於搭配`ComponentsUrl`屬性。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.ComponentsLocation%2A> is not specified, `HomeSite` is used by default.
trans-unit.target: 如果未指定 <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.ComponentsLocation%2A>，預設會使用 `HomeSite`。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URL containing the installation prerequisites.
The URL containing the installation prerequisites.
trans-unit.target: 包含安裝必要條件的 URL。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the bootstrapper copies all output files to the path specified in the <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.OutputPath" /> property.

<see langword="true" /> if the bootstrapper should copy all output files to the path specified in the <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.OutputPath" /> property; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果啟動載入器應該複製所有輸出檔案到 <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.OutputPath" /> 屬性中指定的路徑，則為 <see langword="true" />；否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default value of this parameter is `true`.
trans-unit.target: 此參數的預設值為 `true`。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the culture to use for the bootstrapper UI and installation prerequisites.
The culture to use for the bootstrapper UI and installation prerequisites.
trans-unit.target: 用於啟動載入器 UI 和安裝必要條件的文化特性。

trans-unit.source: If the specified culture is unavailabe, the task uses the value of the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.FallbackCulture%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的文化特性時，工作會使用值<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.GenerateBootstrapper.FallbackCulture%2A>屬性。

trans-unit.source: Executes the <c>GenerateBootstrapper</c> task.
<see langword="true" /> if the task execution succeeded; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
Gets or sets the secondary culture to use for the bootstraper UI and installation prerequisites.
The secondary culture to use for the bootstraper UI and installation prerequisites.
trans-unit.target: 用於啟動載入器 UI 和安裝必要條件的次要文化特性。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the location to copy setup.exe and all package files.
The location to copy setup.exe and all package files.
trans-unit.target: 要複製 setup.exe 和所有封裝檔案的位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the location of all available prerequisite packages.
The location of all available prerequisite packages.
trans-unit.target: 所有可用的必要條件封裝位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URL to provide should the bootstrapper installation fail.
The URL to provide should the bootstrapper installation fail.
trans-unit.target: 啟動載入器安裝失敗時要提供的 URL。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the bootstrapper performs XSD validation on the specified input bootstrapper items.
<see langword="true" /> if the bootstrapper performs XSD validation on the specified input bootstrapper items; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> 如果啟動載入器會在指定的輸入啟動載入器項目; 上執行 XSD 驗證否則， <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default value of this parameter is `false`.
trans-unit.target: 此參數的預設值為 `false`。

trans-unit.source: The Visual Studio version, in the form <major build.minor build>, for example "4.0".
Returns <see cref="T:System.String" />.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:System.String" />。
